# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Dark Pattern Detector — Environment Variables
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# HOW TO SET UP:
# 1. Copy this file: copy .env.example .env  (Windows)
#                    cp .env.example .env    (Mac/Linux)
# 2. Fill in your Gemini API key below
# 3. Save the file
# 4. NEVER commit .env to GitHub (it's in .gitignore)
#
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── REQUIRED ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your FREE Gemini API key (takes 30 seconds):
# 1. Go to: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Sign in with Google
# 3. Click "Create API Key"
# 4. Paste it below
GEMINI_API_KEY=paste_your_gemini_api_key_here

# ── DATABASE ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: SQLite (zero setup, works immediately locally)
# For PostgreSQL locally, uncomment and fill:
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://darkpattern_user:darkpattern_pass@localhost:5432/darkpattern_db
#
# On Render: DATABASE_URL is set automatically — don't touch it

# ── FRONTEND API URL ─────────────────────────────────────
# Default: http://localhost:8000/api (local dev)
# On Render: Set this to your deployed backend URL
# API_BASE=https://dark-pattern-backend.onrender.com/api
